&lt;/div&gt;



  &lt;div&gt;
    &lt;div class="section-tag"&gt;Core Logic&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;h2 class="section-title"&gt;Method Breakdown&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="method-list"&gt;
  &lt;div class="mini-card"&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;1. LiDAR Processing&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Filter invalid range values and optionally constrain the field of view.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Stabilize scan interpretation for local decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Prepare structured observations for downstream free-space analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="mini-card"&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;2. Gap Detection&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Detect candidate traversable regions from local scan geometry.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Measure angular width, clearance, and relative safety of each gap.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Reject weak candidates that could increase crash risk.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="mini-card"&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;3. Goal Generation&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Select a target direction or local waypoint from the chosen gap.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Bias the choice toward forward progress and smoother future motion.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Reduce oscillation through practical heuristics and filtering.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="mini-card"&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;4. Pure Pursuit Control&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Convert local targets into Ackermann steering commands.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Adjust speed according to curvature, stability, or risk level.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Maintain smooth closed-loop behavior across straightaways and turns.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="results-note"&gt;
  A strong improvement for the final version would be to add one small diagram under each block, such as a LiDAR polar plot, a gap visualization, and a waypoint-to-curvature sketch.
&lt;/div&gt;



  &lt;div&gt;
    &lt;div class="section-tag"&gt;Execution Plan&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;h2 class="section-title"&gt;Team Plan & Task Allocation&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p class="section-lead"&gt;
  To move efficiently from simulator validation to real vehicle deployment, the project is divided into tightly coupled technical tracks.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="allocation-grid"&gt;
  &lt;div class="member-card"&gt;
    &lt;div class="member-role"&gt;Perception&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;[Teammate 1 Name]&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Focus:&lt;/strong&gt; LiDAR processing and gap detection&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Filter scan noise and build robust free-space interpretation.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Implement detection logic for safe, traversable local gaps.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="member-card"&gt;
    &lt;div class="member-role"&gt;Control&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;[Teammate 2 Name]&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Focus:&lt;/strong&gt; Pure Pursuit and speed policy&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Transform local targets into stable steering outputs.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Tune control behavior for faster and smoother lap performance.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="member-card"&gt;
    &lt;div class="member-role"&gt;Localization&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;[Teammate 3 Name]&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Focus:&lt;/strong&gt; Odometry, TF, and environment understanding&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Maintain correct frame relationships and motion context.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Support future track-aware improvements if mapping is introduced.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="member-card"&gt;
    &lt;div class="member-role"&gt;Integration&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;[Teammate 4 Name]&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Focus:&lt;/strong&gt; ROS 2 integration and hardware deployment&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Ensure node communication and stable system bring-up.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;Lead the simulator-to-Jetson deployment path for Milestone 3.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
